title: Strictly Come Dancing: Anthony Ogogo challenges judges to enter boxing ring a... - Thetelegraphand Argus
text:
Anthony Ogogo said he would like to take on the Strictly judges in the boxing ring after they were "harsh" on him as he became the second contestant to leave this year's competition. The Olympic boxer, 26, failed to punch above his weight as he performed a paso doble to Eye Of The Tiger from the movie Rocky.
 Thetelegraphand Argus.
